      "author": "olrenso",
      "description": "# What's new in v1.2.0\r\n- You can now search through the [Surfing plugin](https://github.com/PKM-er/Obsidian-Surfing) directly from the Home tab by using the filter keys `surfing` or `web`.\r\n- Omnisearch is now also available with the filter keys `omnisearch` and `omni`.\r\n- If you enable Omnisearch as the default search behaviour, you can now still use the filter keys to search specific file types or extensions.\r\n- Added support for the new Bookmarks plugin that will replace the Starred plugin.\r\n- Added filter key (`canvas`) to search canvas notes/files.",
