      "author": "olrenso",
      "description": "# What's new in v1.1.0\r\n- You can now embed the search bar in any note (#8)\r\n- Added support for Obsidian mobile (#10)\r\n- Added ability to set custom icons for starred files (#3)\r\n- Added option to delay the search results (#12)\r\n- You can now disable the automatic opening of the Home tab. This allows using of plugins like [Surfing](https://github.com/PKM-er/Obsidian-Surfing), [Homepage](https://github.com/mirnovov/obsidian-homepage), or [New tab default page](https://github.com/chrisgrieser/new-tab-default-page). You can manually open a new Home tab through the command palette.",
